reviewText: It lived up to it's name about money making opportunities in the 1950s,but the film was a bit too long. It made it's main point halfway through. Was longer than it needed to be.

Ok video about the 1950s. A bit heavy on the graphics but has some good footage. Showed it in my 11th grade class. I wish there was a more comprehensive 1950s DVD with music, culture, film, media, news all wrapped into one.
